api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://e2e-dictionary.p.rapidapi.com/dictionary/word"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "e2e-dictionary.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

import requests

url = "https://e2e-dictionary.p.rapidapi.com/dictionary/{word}"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "e2e-dictionary.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
